All 4 fields are optional. CherryVis will skip tasks if malformed.

--- UPCs - Unit Probability Commands ------------------------------------------

Rarely needed unless you want advanced overlays.

{
  "id": 123,
  "generation_frame": 50,
  "consumer": "ModuleName",
  "command": {
      "attack": 1.0,
      "move": 0.0,
      "gather": 0.0
  },
  "targets": [
      {
        "type": "unit",
        "unit_id": 83,
        "score": 1.0
      }
  ]
}

